4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp where students master essential technologies like JavaScript and Python to kickstart their tech careers. This intensive program lasts 18 weeks, featuring 3 classes weekly with a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. No prior coding experience is required, and classes are available in both English and Spanish. Participants will learn to build websites, develop apps, and enhance functionality using APIs, culminating in a personal project for hands-on experience. Upon completion, graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certification. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop